===Noun===
# A [[brag]], a loud appraisal of oneself
# (''[[squash]]'') A shot where the ball [[bounce]]s off at least 2 walls and the front wall

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[omakehu]] (1)

===Verb===
# to [[brag]]; to talk loudly in praise of oneself
# (''squash'') To play a boast shot

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[kerskailla]] ([[joku|jollakin]]) (1), [[kerskua]] ([[joku|jostakin]]) (1), [[rehennellä]] (1), [[leuhkia]] (1)
*French: [[vanter]] (1)

